1
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:56,000
Whose red sports car was that?

2
00:00:57,079 --> 00:00:58,200
I don't know.

3
00:00:59,039 --> 00:01:01,560
Niannian said Di Fu rented it.

4
00:01:02,079 --> 00:01:03,359
But I asked Di Fu,

5
00:01:03,359 --> 00:01:05,319
and Di Fu said she never rented a car.

6
00:01:06,519 --> 00:01:10,680
That's when I knew Niannian was lying to me.

7
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:12,799
Niannian probably didn't want you to worry,

8
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,519
so she lied to you.

9
00:01:14,799 --> 00:01:16,359
But I am her mother.

10
00:01:16,599 --> 00:01:18,359
She should have told me.

11
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:19,280
What happened next?

12
00:01:21,879 --> 00:01:25,400
Later, I cornered Niannian at home

13
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:28,879
and asked if she had a boyfriend.

14
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:30,799
Not only did she refuse to say,

15
00:01:30,799 --> 00:01:32,400
but she also had a big fight with me.

16
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:36,319
Niannian left home after arguing with me that day.

17
00:01:37,319 --> 00:01:39,200
That day was her birthday.

18
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:41,519
She never came home again.

19
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:46,400
Tell me the truth.

20
00:01:46,799 --> 00:01:48,120
What happened that day?

21
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:51,400
I... I don't know.

22
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,760
Tell me!

23
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:54,719
Calm down.

24
00:01:54,719 --> 00:01:56,120
Let's save Zhao Qihai first.

25
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,040
If he dies,

26
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,000
the nature of this changes.

27
00:01:58,319 --> 00:01:59,719
We won't be able to help you even if we want to.

28
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,319
If you become a murderer,

29
00:02:01,519 --> 00:02:02,560
how will you save your daughter?

30
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:04,519
I really don't know.

31
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,159
Inspector Qi.

32
00:02:13,719 --> 00:02:15,560
Thanks to you dressing his wound,

33
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:17,080
will he die?

34
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:19,400
A Si has made the call.

35
00:02:19,719 --> 00:02:20,599
The ambulance can't get in.

36
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,319
I don't want him to die.

37
00:02:22,919 --> 00:02:24,120
If he dies,

38
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:26,560
Auntie Ma really becomes a murderer.

39
00:02:27,319 --> 00:02:29,680
A Si, you've got good moves.

40
00:02:31,599 --> 00:02:32,960
I once taught myself some

41
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,800
simple self-defense moves.

42
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:38,400
Besides, being around Madam and Mr. Zhao,

43
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,680
I have to know a little.

44
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,120
Inspector Qi

45
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:57,919
What about Auntie Ma?

46
00:02:58,599 --> 00:02:59,800
Let her calm down first.

47
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:01,120
We'll talk to her later.

48
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,520
Helicopter... can't the helicopter take off?

49
00:03:07,919 --> 00:03:09,800
Louder, I can't hear you. Hello?

50
00:03:11,479 --> 00:03:12,400
No signal again.

51
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:16,439
Helicopters are dangerous in this weather.

52
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:17,680
Mr. Tan

53
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:19,800
Please be patient.

54
00:03:24,639 --> 00:03:25,280
Mr. Fang

55
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:26,680
How are you doing?

56
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,159
I... I won't die.

57
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,159
What is it?

58
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:39,759
Mr. Fang hasn't finished speaking.

59
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:42,520
What is there to say?

60
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,319
On Niannian's birthday...

61
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:46,520
what exactly happened?

62
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:56,560
It was Niannian's birthday.

63
00:03:58,039 --> 00:03:58,639
I...

64
00:03:59,199 --> 00:03:59,800
Di Fu...

65
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,840
and a few friends were having dinner together.

66
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,960
Later, after dinner...

67
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:04,800
they partied too hard.

68
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:07,400
Then Niannian took too much.

69
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:08,919
And she passed out.

70
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:10,159
We thought she was dead.

71
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:11,639
Just then...

72
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,240
her mother...

73
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,479
that... that Ma Shan...

74
00:04:13,719 --> 00:04:14,520
called her.

75
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,800
We were scared at the time...

76
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,680
scared of being exposed.

77
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,800
So we turned off her phone.

78
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:19,399
Then Di Fu told me...

79
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:21,920
to take her to that warehouse in the suburbs...

80
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,879
and deal with her.

81
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,000
I swear!

82
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,720
I only took her to the warehouse.

83
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,879
I really didn't kill her.

84
00:04:28,079 --> 00:04:29,399
Later, she woke up on her own.

85
00:04:29,879 --> 00:04:30,920
And she ran away.

86
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,319
Ran away?

87
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:33,800
Ran away.

88
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,480
When Di Fu and Ma Shan arrived...

89
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,720
she was already gone.

90
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:37,680
Inspector Qi...

91
00:04:37,759 --> 00:04:39,120
I even went looking for her.

92
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,000
I couldn't find her.

93
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,319
I suspect... since there are cliffs all around...

94
00:04:42,319 --> 00:04:43,680
she wasn't thinking clearly...

95
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,120
and accidentally fell off.

96
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:47,560
But Di Fu was the mastermind behind this!

97
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,720
I was forced!

98
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,040
You're lying!

99
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:52,319
I'm not lying! I'm telling the truth!

100
00:04:53,519 --> 00:04:54,000
Missing...

101
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,040
Well, I didn't find her anyway.

102
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:58,439
No sign of her, dead or alive.

103
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,879
Impossible. My sister wouldn't.

104
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:02,360
Everyone.

105
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:03,759
Dinner is ready.

106
00:05:05,439 --> 00:05:06,680
I can't eat.

107
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,480
I'll go check on Ma Shan.

108
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,399
I'll go with you.

109
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,240
What's wrong?

110
00:05:38,959 --> 00:05:40,399
I think I understand.

111
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:42,959
The meaning of these two paintings.

112
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:46,519
This place is magnificent.

113
00:05:47,079 --> 00:05:48,000
Just like heaven.

114
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:50,600
But who knows

115
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:53,079
how much filth is hidden behind it.

116
00:05:56,199 --> 00:05:57,000
As the saying goes,

117
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,480
one thought is heaven,

118
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:00,800
one thought is hell.

119
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:03,839
Inspector Qi,

120
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:06,199
I'm really worried.

121
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:09,319
If my sister is truly guilty of a heinous crime,

122
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,000
what should I do?

123
00:06:12,319 --> 00:06:14,120
You are you, and she is she.

124
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,199
But I always feel

125
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:20,160
my sister didn't truly want to kill anyone.

126
00:06:21,879 --> 00:06:23,279
But that someone forced her.

127
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,920
Then who do you think

128
00:06:28,879 --> 00:06:30,519
forced her?

129
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,199
Everyone here.

130
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:33,920
Including you and me.

131
00:06:35,639 --> 00:06:36,519
I am her sister.

132
00:06:37,079 --> 00:06:39,600
She always told me she wanted to be someone.

133
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,480
To reunite us sisters,

134
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,800
and give me the best life.

135
00:06:44,439 --> 00:06:45,160
But what about me?

136
00:06:45,519 --> 00:06:46,480
You are a police officer.

137
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,519
If she committed a crime,

138
00:06:49,319 --> 00:06:50,680
the police will definitely arrest her.

139
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,160
What about the others?

140
00:06:56,079 --> 00:06:57,279
I don't know about them.

141
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,720
You'll have to investigate that yourself.

142
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,720
I understand what you mean.

143
00:07:03,759 --> 00:07:05,040
You want to tell me

144
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:07,199
that your sister was forced to commit crimes.

145
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,560
No need to answer.

146
00:07:10,079 --> 00:07:10,759
You know,

147
00:07:10,959 --> 00:07:12,920
whether you answer yes or no,

148
00:07:13,399 --> 00:07:15,199
it sounds like you're trying to clear your sister's name.

149
00:07:16,439 --> 00:07:17,639
In the eyes of you police,

150
00:07:18,279 --> 00:07:19,759
does everyone look like a bad person?

151
00:07:20,319 --> 00:07:21,160
That's not true.

152
00:07:21,879 --> 00:07:22,480
There are good people.

153
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,240
Who?

154
00:07:24,199 --> 00:07:24,839
My son.

155
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:28,759
See?

156
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:31,160
From my subjective point of view,

157
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:33,160
I believe my son is a good person.

158
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,519
Just like you.

159
00:07:35,199 --> 00:07:36,800
From your subjective point of view,

160
00:07:37,319 --> 00:07:38,920
you also believe your sister is innocent.

161
00:07:39,399 --> 00:07:40,480
That she was forced.

162
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,480
So who should we believe?

163
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,519
Evidence.

164
00:07:46,319 --> 00:07:47,120
The truth.

165
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:54,720
Ms. Ma,

166
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:56,480
I want to tell you,

167
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,920
I will definitely help you find your daughter.

168
00:08:00,879 --> 00:08:01,759
But there are some things

169
00:08:01,759 --> 00:08:03,360
I hope you can tell me the truth about.

170
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:04,639
Okay.

171
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,519
Before Di Fu's accident,

172
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,959
did she say anything to you?

173
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:16,839
A few days before Di Fu's accident,

174
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,800
she brought me here.

175
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:25,560
Di Fu.

176
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:26,920
Godmother.

177
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,279
Di Fu,

178
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,279
thank you for worrying about my loneliness

179
00:08:39,399 --> 00:08:40,399
and bringing me here.

180
00:08:41,279 --> 00:08:42,759
No need to be so polite with me.

181
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:44,759
Godmother,

182
00:08:46,759 --> 00:08:47,960
if I'm no longer around,

183
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,799
will there be no one to take care of you?

184
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:52,360
Don't talk nonsense.

185
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:55,039
I've already lost one daughter.

186
00:08:55,399 --> 00:08:56,799
I don't want to lose another.

187
00:08:57,639 --> 00:08:58,360
I'm just saying,

188
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,320
if

189
00:09:00,519 --> 00:09:02,279
something happens to me one day,

190
00:09:02,639 --> 00:09:04,000
please don't be sad.

191
00:09:04,559 --> 00:09:06,399
I've arranged everything for you.

192
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,559
A lawyer will contact you.

193
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:11,240
Why are you saying these things out of nowhere?

194
00:09:11,759 --> 00:09:12,799
That's such bad luck.

195
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:14,480
Godmother,

196
00:09:16,559 --> 00:09:18,279
there's something I want to tell you.

197
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:19,480
Tell me.

198
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,519
Di Fu really has leukemia.

199
00:09:37,679 --> 00:09:40,279
Yes, she showed me the medical report.

200
00:09:40,639 --> 00:09:43,480
Three days later, something happened to her and Mr. Zhao.

201
00:09:45,159 --> 00:09:46,600
I was very sad at the time.

202
00:09:46,799 --> 00:09:48,159
The police were solving the case.

203
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:50,120
So I went back to my own house.

204
00:09:51,679 --> 00:09:52,720
A day later,

205
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,720
Lawyer Luo found me.

206
00:09:55,279 --> 00:09:56,279
Saying Di Fu

207
00:09:57,519 --> 00:09:59,159
left me an inheritance.

208
00:10:03,919 --> 00:10:06,960
After that, I received a letter.

209
00:10:16,919 --> 00:10:17,960
What did the letter say?

210
00:10:21,279 --> 00:10:24,720
It said Niannian was already dead.

211
00:10:25,519 --> 00:10:27,799
And no one knew where her body was disposed of.

212
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:30,840
Fang Qiu,

213
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,399
Tan Tian,

214
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,200
and Zhao Qihai...

215
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,120
were all involved in this.

216
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:39,320
If I wanted to find my daughter's body

217
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,279
and avenge her,

218
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:43,200
I had to make good use of this opportunity.

219
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:45,799
The opportunity of the will reading.

220
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:48,159
To avenge my daughter.

221
00:10:48,159 --> 00:10:49,720
The knockout drug in our food...

222
00:10:50,399 --> 00:10:51,120
you prepared it?

223
00:10:52,759 --> 00:10:54,120
You came up with all these plans?

224
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:58,360
I'm sorry, Inspector Qi, Miss Li.

225
00:10:59,559 --> 00:11:00,399
I just wanted...

226
00:11:00,399 --> 00:11:01,639
before I die...

227
00:11:02,279 --> 00:11:04,480
to personally kill those

228
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:06,799
murderers who killed my daughter.

229
00:11:06,799 --> 00:11:07,559
Auntie Ma.

230
00:11:07,759 --> 00:11:08,879
I am a police officer.

231
00:11:10,639 --> 00:11:11,639
Trust me this once.

232
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,759
Let me handle the rest.

233
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:17,879
Inspector Qi.

234
00:11:22,919 --> 00:11:24,120
Do you believe Ma Shan?

235
00:11:28,559 --> 00:11:30,000
She has no reason to lie anymore.

236
00:11:31,279 --> 00:11:32,279
Then who do you think

237
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:35,840
sent her that letter?

238
00:11:38,279 --> 00:11:38,799
I don't know.

239
00:11:38,799 --> 00:11:39,360
Di Fu?

240
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:40,480
It was Di Fu.

241
00:11:40,759 --> 00:11:41,320
Zhao Qihai.
